Glentree Residential School is a world of its own, where your child will be nurtured and encouraged to be all he or she aspires to be. We do it by integrating STAY, PLAY and LEARN. When it comes to STAY – we offer world-class boarding facilities. For PLAY – we provide Residential Sports Academy supported by Professional Coaches. And for LEARN – Glentree Academy is one of the leading CBSE schools in Bangalore, and our motto is – “Learning for Life”.
